last_episode_to_air.name: Obstacle Race
last_episode_to_air.overview: It's the start of another day in Biggleton and out in the park Momo the Athlete is busy getting ready for an important sporting event - the Big Biggleton Obstacle Race. After polishing the trophy Momo races off to tell the people of Biggleton about the race. But when the racers assemble for the race, Nurse Oscar notices that all the obstacles are missing. Momo the Athlete has been so busy telling everyone about the race, she's forgotten to set up any obstacles.
